              "linkId": "650226868798",
              "type": "display",
              "text": "As evidence, you may include a URL along with details from Dropbox, Box, Google Drive, Portal, JIRA, Confluence, GitHub, or any other storage platform that holds documentation for the most recently completed penetration test results details.",
